{"tid":1017249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★綜援又贏！政府將資助接受社會福利人士 購買數碼電視機","createTime":"2019-02-11T10:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T13:23:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7ec06750b4d54db38d9ffccb4cf3ac017fbf58","tid":1017249,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"終止模擬廣播預計有18萬戶受影響，將透過關愛基金，資助其中16萬受影響用戶購買電視機或機頂盒。<br />\n<br />\n被問到用公帑資助買電視機會否補貼電視生產商，邱指參考外國經驗，都會資助有需要人士買機頂盒，但港府想做得更好，故提供資助予合資格人士買電視機或換機頂盒。他指，詳情稍後始公布，但<span style=\"color: red;\">合資格人士主要包括正接受政府社會福利支援的人士，他們申請時不需入息審查</span>。另外又會與關愛基金商討，並參考基金以往如何定義合資格的受資助人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190211/bkn-20190211150242241-0211_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190211%2Fbkn-20190211150242241-0211_00822_001.html&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu10HQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=07a9180d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190211/bkn-20190211150242241-0211_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d6b8f6b2040eb4f85096418345d669c389e6ce8e","tid":1017249,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"2e1b16f1e015ab362daa15cb1de9807454c05306","tid":1017249,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:13:35.000Z","msg":"不需入息審查<br />\n不需入息審查<br />\n不需入息審查"},{"pid":"95193246f5d0ea85276c131153d7006a75daffc7","tid":1017249,"uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"只准買支那牌子電視機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee24e8a1113fa5b084471db198152504587b6f1","tid":1017249,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95193246f5d0ea85276c131153d7006a75daffc7","tid":1017249,"uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-